Subject: invitation letter for marriage From: "GradProSkills" <gradproskills@concordia.ca> Date: 2014/1/6 17:39 To: wkkustc@gmail.com
Dear Loren and James,
It is a big honor for us to ask for your presence on the upcoming marriage of our eldest son Randy Jones to his beautiful fiance Joahnna Reeves. The matromony is scheduled on June 12, 2009 at 8:00 AM in place just near us.
We would be very delighted if you will be here two days prior to the said date for you to be able to take part in the pre-nuptial activities. It will also give you a chance to speak with the couple since you have witnessed how they have grown to be wonderful individuals.
Hope to receive a possitive feedback from you.
Best Regards, Anna and Simon
